Package com.vmware.vcenter.namespaces

The com.vmware.vcenter.namespaces package provides interfaces for managing namespaces related methods.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Access
    The Access interface provides methods to manage access control of subjects on namespaces.
    Access.CreateInvocation
    Invocable that represents the Access#create vAPI operation.
    Access.DeleteInvocation
    Invocable that represents the Access#delete vAPI operation.
    Access.GetInvocation
    Invocable that represents the Access#get vAPI operation.
    Access.SetInvocation
    Invocable that represents the Access#set vAPI operation.
    AccessTypes
    Defines the data types of the Access API service.

    NamespaceSelfService.DeactivateInvocation
    Invocable that represents the NamespaceSelfService#deactivate vAPI operation.
    NamespaceSelfService.GetInvocation
    Invocable that represents the NamespaceSelfService#get vAPI operation.
    NamespaceSelfService.ListInvocation
    Invocable that represents the NamespaceSelfService#list vAPI operation.
    NamespaceSelfServiceTypes
    Defines the data types of the NamespaceSelfService API service.
    NamespaceTemplates
    The NamespaceTemplates interface provides methods to create and update namespace templates on a cluster.
